Newform #2 (2.0.56.1-7.1b)
 - Genus character value: +1 (trivial)
 - Dimension: 2
 - Newform is twisted base-change but not base-change
 - Newform is not unramified self-twist
 - Sign of functional equation = +1
 - Principal Hecke field k_f = Q(b) = Q[X]/(X^2-X-4)
